text: Ocean Springs is a city in Jackson County, Mississippi, USA, about 2 miles east of Biloxi. It is part of the Pascagoula, Mississippi Metropolitan Statistical Area. The population was 18,429 at the 2020 census. == References == == Other websites == * Ocean Springs Archives * Ocean Springs Chamber of Commerce * Scharr-Ello Music Foundation of Ocean Springs Category:Cities in Mississippi
